Comment: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:46.73,Title,,0,0,0,,Eternal Friends! \NThe Vowed Bell Echoes Across the Mighty Seas!!
Comment: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:36.02,Title,,0,0,0,,Angel Island Obliterated! \NThe Horror of the Raigo's Advent!!
