Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The commodore seems sad...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.01,0:02:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Just after he made such a \Ngreat friend all the way out here...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this makes any sense!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We set sail first thing tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.25,0:02:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But the villagers are so \Nbloodthirsty we can't go near 'em,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.24,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention, the bell didn't ring again today...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't show your face around me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want your wife to end up a widow?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.48,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a heartrending way to leave...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mousse-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.19,0:03:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Botanist, my ass!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.89,0:03:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Noland!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.73,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If these are the victims of your "advancements,"
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.77,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,then we should never have accepted you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindred Trees?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.74,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.95,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that all the spirits of our \Nancestors who died on this island
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.23,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,are guided to them by the bell \Nso they can settle inside them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.96,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All of our ancestors who lived on \Nthe island since the age of Shandora
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.46,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,watch over us from those sacred, white trees.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.77,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kindred Woods are so \Ntruly important to us Shandians
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.23,0:04:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've protected them as much \Nas we've protected our own lives!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And we chopped them all down...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.91,0:04:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The warriors were angry and \Ninstantly took up their weapons...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}must{\i0} drive them off this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.42,0:04:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...but since you had saved so \Nmany of the villagers' lives...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.01,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. \NSo that attitude was anger they couldn't act on...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was just for tree research...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you didn't know...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers' anger won't go away now...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I thought I would at least ask why...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...before you left...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.37,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Someone help with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Trees where ancestors' spirits dwell...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get it all on board now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.83,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea. We've done something \Nthat can never be taken back...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers are right to be angry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Commodore! \NWe had no choice, given—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.05,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No excuses! I only did what satisfied me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.26,0:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told that aside from \Nproclaiming the city's existence,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.61,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that bell also served to guide their ancestors' spirits to the island.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.40,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we cut down those trees!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no reason to be forgiven!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.04,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Leave all the gold behind?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.38,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Noland and his men are preparing to leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mousse! Where were you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What if...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.07,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you knew a single, \Nimportant tree was tainted by poison...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.41,0:06:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And that its poison would \Neventually spread into the forest,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,affect people, and kill an island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you knew beforehand?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was us...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.93,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What would {\i1}we{\i0} do with that single, important tree?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.94,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Go quickly and stop them!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool! You know what they've done!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we part now, we'll regret it for the rest of our lives!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally made such a dear friend,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and we Shandians owe them so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're going to leave them \Nhurt for the rest of their lives!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.71,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably sound like an excuse,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but for the commodore's honor, I must say this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those woods of yours were already dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.51,0:07:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The true horror of the Kinetsu plague \Nis that it can also infect plant life.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}because{\i0} he knew this
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that the commodore pleaded with \Nyou without regard for his own life.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,From people to forest, forest to people...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.74,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Several small islands have been \Ndestroyed in exactly that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing to worry about now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.25,0:07:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We finished checking the entire forest yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that we cut down your beloved woods
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,without knowing or explaining...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd probably still be unforgivable \Neven with an explanation,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.53,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but a botanist would never harm \Na forest without good reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.39,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The commodore doesn't hate \Ngods and spirits and stuff...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.48,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that he always knows what's most important.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.24,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That means... they did it for us?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Noland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone have everything?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All except one thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit mopin'! Just forget about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.68,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It's time to go! \NEveryone to your positions!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.89,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now heading back to the Lvneel Kingdom!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Noland!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've committed such a sin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.40,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait! Noland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.50,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the bell ringing?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Noland-{\i0}san{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.89,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Louder! So Noland and the others can hear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore! Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.65,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Noland!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calgara...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.42,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back again!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Noland...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.18,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep on ringing the bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.23,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So that your ship won't get \Nlost at sea when you return...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.28,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you won't lose sight \Nof this island during a storm...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.28,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ring this bell and wait for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.92,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again someday for sure! \NFriend of mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.51,0:11:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can... come back again?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.27,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll be back! I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.49,0:11:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again someday for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.43,0:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There once was a man named Montblanc Noland,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.31,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from a kingdom in the northern seas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.10,0:11:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Noland the Explorer always told \Nstories of incredible adventures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.78,0:11:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the villagers could never \Ntell if they were true or not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.74,0:12:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, Noland returned from a \Njourney and reported to the king.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It stands all the more proudly and beautifully in ruin!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.79,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This city is named Shandora! \NThe term "city of gold" fits it like none other!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.93,0:12:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mary Geoise has finally granted us \Npermission to enter the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, I wish to send you on another mission.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it would be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.35,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I've decided my soldiers will \Njoin you on this journey, as will I.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Calgara!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're off to ring the bell, right? I'll help!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nola. You've sure settled into these ruins!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Say! When do you suppose Noland-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others will come?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.47,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you ever ask when you come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.69,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be so easy for him to come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.77,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born in the far northern seas. \NHe also has a family back home.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But he did promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.15,0:13:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we keep ringing this bell here, \Nhe'll show up sooner or later.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.58,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?! This looks bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Seto! We have to protect the village!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.53,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does the island suddenly end here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! You lied to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this gold of yours?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where did the village go?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened to this island?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.75,0:14:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calgara! If you're alive, let me hear it! \NThe sound of the gold bell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.39,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Answer me, fire of Shandora!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Noland's public execution's about to start!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This way, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Six years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.11,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a giant city of gold on \Nthe Grand Line island of Jaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of gold does exist!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.24,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hear from one of your crewmen.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this man telling the truth?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.00,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's an absolute lie.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.76,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Noland-{\i1}san{\i0} is a liar?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then were {\i1}all{\i0} his stories fake?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.17,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's messed up! He lied to the \Nwhole kingdom and acted like a hero!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that witness?! \NHe's not part of our crew!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.14,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Calgara and the others?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore! What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize them!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Men...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.20,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For his heinous lies, \NMontblanc Noland is hereby sentenced
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to death by beheading!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a liar!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The commodore'd never lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.84,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! Liar! Liar! Liar!...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God! It's a giant island of Vearth!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.56,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Did you hear that? \NThe singing voice of this beautiful Vearth...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.61,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is truly the birth of holy land. \NThat is where I must live!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?! I can't breathe well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourselves together!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourselves together!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tend to the wounded! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Calgara! Intruders!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.72,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby claim this Vearth as mine! I am God!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God, my ass!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop them, warriors!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot let this land be taken away!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We made a promise, Noland...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.86,0:17:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That we would meet again someday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.45,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calgara... Where are you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.35,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you return to Jaya, what will \Nyou think when you see we're gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.25,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on a little longer! \NI'll let you know that "we are here"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you alive?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have so much to tell you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calgara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm only concerned for your well-being...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.35,0:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's meet again on the same land someday, Noland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.78,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Light the fire of Shandora!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Warrior Calgara continued to shout.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once would've been enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.20,0:18:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For he believed the fire of Shandora \Nwould echo and let all know that,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"We are here!"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.55,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But the bell never once rang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.26,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was later told to our \Nvillage by sailors from the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.22,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Noland, to whom we owe so much, \Nhad such pride for our city
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.29,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that he refused to deny Shandora's \Nexistence and died known as a liar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was already too late,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.36,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for Great Warrior Calgara had died \Nhonorably in battle here in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Never being able to convey his message...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.97,0:19:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Great Warrior Calgara's greatest regret.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it could still reach him?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.05,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That bell! If we rang it now, \Nwould its sound reach Noland?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good question...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}are{\i0} close to Heaven...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.19,0:19:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper! We'll die if we don't escape now!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.82,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wyper...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.65,0:19:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eneru...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.24,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives you the right \Nto take everything away?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sky! God's domain!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is an eyesore!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.67,0:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The people, the trees, the land! \NReturn to where you belong!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.05,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let everything rain into the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.89,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel Island won't last much longer!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of injured people!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them into boats, then give them first aid!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, into the ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.36,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.45,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get chills when I imagine that \Ngirl's speech being any later!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she all right?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's far above now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.76,0:20:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time until his ship reaches the top of the vine.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.59,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it Eneru wants there?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.14,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A gold bell at the top.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.31,0:20:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The scurrying angels are like a \Nline of ants that's been disturbed!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.40,0:21:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to where you belong, Skypiea!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.29,0:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A hole in the White-White Sea?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.45,0:21:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need for good old God's Shrine either!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor for the city of Shandora below it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.60,0:21:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is but one thing left \Nin this land that I want!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.42,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The golden grand belfry!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Two voices, at this final stage?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.66,0:21:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! How can he run so fast?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Be all right!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.08,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't let you have the golden bell, Eneru!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then! \NTime for that eyesore of an island to disappear!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! The clouds are changing shape!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.29,0:23:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have your way, Eneru!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.71,0:23:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no stopping this Raigo!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.21,0:23:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to escape, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.84,0:23:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can just catch him...!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.48,0:23:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel Island Obliterated! \NThe Horror of the Raigo's Advent!!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
